### 上传文档（txt/md/pdf/docx）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="refund-policy.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

< ./refund-policy.md
--WebAppBoundary--

### 列出文档
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/documents

### RAG 问答
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "退款政策是什么？",
  "topK": 5
}

### 删除文档
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/rag/documents/1
